<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Vegetarian Diet Plan for Weight Gain</h1>

    <h2>General Guidelines</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Caloric Surplus: Aim for 300-500 extra calories daily.</li>
        <li>Frequent Meals: Eat 5-6 smaller meals/snacks throughout the day.</li>
        <li>Nutrient-Dense Foods: Focus on whole, high-calorie foods.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sample Meal Plan</h2>

    <h3>Breakfast</h3>
    <p>Oatmeal made with whole milk, topped with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>2 tablespoons of almond butter</li>
        <li>A handful of mixed nuts and berries</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Morning Snack</h3>
    <p>Smoothie made with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>1 cup of almond milk</li>
        <li>1 scoop of plant-based protein powder</li>
        <li>1 banana and a tablespoon of peanut butter</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Lunch</h3>
    <p>Chickpea salad with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Quinoa, cucumbers, tomatoes, and feta cheese</li>
        <li>Olive oil and lemon dressing</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Afternoon Snack</h3>
    <p>Hummus with carrot and cucumber sticks</p>

    <h3>Dinner</h3>
    <p>Lentil stew with mixed vegetables and whole grain bread</p>

    <h3>Evening Snack</h3>
    <p>A bowl of mixed nuts and dried fruits</p>
</div>

